<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Gal In Ka Dawn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginnan vankhuo galin ka dawn,
 Khawvel gimum thuok zote chu,
 Naubang nui siusieu in ka mui,
 A kipahnau zaila gihawih,
 Ka lunggil ah daibang a cham,
 Gam nuom tunkal ka ngaklah ie.

[V2]
 Ei hun enin van Lal thiengtho,
 Mi lungsiet um leh hatlo hi;
 Zinmang in henkawl ei buh hi,
 Na gam hung tun nuom mahleng le,
 Thimna leh lungkhamna haw hin,
 Sunni chengin ei bawm.

[V3]
 2. Ngaklah manin tung thei puong ie,
 Tih lunggila ka gel phat leh;
 Lungkham in naubang ka kap hi,
 Tun kal ka ngaklah ziek ahi,
 Lalpa, Na gam thiengtho tak chu,
 Ngaia kapin zailan ka awi.

[V4]
 3. Awla bangkim ka gel gelin,
 Albang ka vaih dan ka kihei;
 Ka kah khawsawtna ding chauh in;
 Kaplai naubanga nuihna ding,
 Nuoi simlei ah mu zo puong ie,
 Ka hun ngai lothei puoi Lalpa

[V5]
 4. Kaplai naubang nui thei puong ie,
 Lalpa, nei hung puih mahin chuh,
 Ka lungkham vanah bei tan a,
 Ka umdan khuo'n a lel ma chun,
 Van gam tunkal ngaklah mah leng,
 Lalpa hung tung thei puong ie maw ?

[V6]
 5. Nuoi simlei gimum ahin le,
 Lalpa naubang a nei puih chun;
 Bangdin albang in ka vai dem?
 Nei umpih hi tih ka hetin,
 Kaplai hi naubang a nui in,
 Nuoi simlei gimum a chawmsak.</lyrics>
<author>V.T. Kappu</author>
<hymn_number>241</hymn_number>
</song>